1:
Praise Yahweh.
\q Praise Yahweh, you in the heavens;
\q praise him, you in the heights.
\q
2:
Praise him, all his angels;
\q praise him, all his angel armies.
4:
Praise him, highest heaven
\q and you waters that are above the sky.
5:
Let them praise the name of Yahweh,
\q for he gave the command, and they were created.
\q
6:
He has also established them forever and ever;
\q he issued a decree that will never change.
7:
Praise him from the earth,
\q you sea monsters and all ocean depths,
\q
8:
fire and hail, snow and clouds,
\q stormy wind fulfilling his word.
9:
Praise him, mountains and all hills,
\q fruit trees and all cedars,
\q
10:
animals wild and tame,
\q creatures that crawl and birds.

 
\q
11:
Praise Yahweh, kings of the earth and all nations,
\q princes and all who govern on the earth,
\q
12:
both young men and young women,
\q elderly and children.
13:
Let them all praise the name of Yahweh,
\q for his name alone is exalted
\q and his glory extends over the earth and the heavens.
\q
14:
He has lifted up the horn of his people
\q for praise from all his faithful ones,
\q the Israelites, the people near to him.
\q Praise Yahweh.
